[The state of Ohio can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5389962,29275. Columbiana county in eastern Ohio can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/ohio-county-map.gif. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ

There are a number of WNV cases being posted on a regular basis this year (2017). With very good vaccines available I cannot figure out why horse owners are failing to vaccinate. There are other diseases that we almost beg for a vaccine to protect our animals and yet when we have one, there are so many people who think there is no need to vaccinate.

The reality is, regardless of where you live, mosquitoes can transmit diseases to your horses. Please use the vaccine. It is effective in preventing the disease. - Mod.TG]
